creditline: Gift of Gus Foster in memory of Ted Hartwell
description: two men (Ramon Muxter and Jeff Petrich) and a blonde woman at a corner table in a bar; man at L has PR arm extended upward and leans over behind woman with hair covering her face; man at R with dark hair gropes woman's breast; received in souvenir white and blue paper folder with reproduction of drawing of couple doing the Mexican hat dance in front
title: Ramon Muxter, Prostitute, and Jeffrey Petrich, Tijuana Mexico, from "Fun, Friends, and Relatives"
